00:22:13,832 --> 00:22:18,303
<font color=#FFFF00>Kalau begitu, bayarlah uang sewa
untuk tanah milik kuil ini!</font>

188
00:22:18,370 --> 00:22:22,113
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau salah paham.
Aku sedang membantumu di sini.</font>

189
00:22:22,207 --> 00:22:24,209
<font color=#FFFF00>Siapa lagi yang mau tinggal di sini?</font>

190
00:22:24,309 --> 00:22:27,552
<font color=#FFFF00>Jika aku tidak menempatinya,
tempat ini bakal membusuk.</font>

191
00:22:27,846 --> 00:22:28,984
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa?</font>

192
00:22:29,047 --> 00:22:30,685
<font color=#FFFF00>Biksu...</font>

193
00:22:31,883 --> 00:22:33,590
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau tahu kenapa aku tinggal di sini?</font>

194
00:22:33,785 --> 00:22:34,889
<font color=#FFFF00>Tidak.</font>

195
00:22:35,787 --> 00:22:39,735
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau sungguh kurang cerdas.
Baiklah, aku akan mengajarimu.</font>

196
00:22:39,991 --> 00:22:43,564
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku bisa melihat rumah
Etsuko-chan dari sini.</font>

197
00:22:47,532 --> 00:22:51,002
<font color=#FFFF00>Ya, aku juga perlu bicara dengannya.</font>

198
00:22:51,703 --> 00:22:53,114
<font color=#FFFF00>Hei...</font>

199
00:22:54,039 --> 00:22:59,717
<font color=#FFFF00>Jangan melakukannya
kalau kau masih betah hidup.</font>

200
00:23:00,045 --> 00:23:04,585
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau mengancamku?!
Sulit dipercaya.</font>

201
00:23:04,883 --> 00:23:09,889
<font color=#FFFF00>Kelakuan Takao juga sulit dipercaya.
Tiba-tiba dia pindah agama jadi Kristen...</font>

202
00:23:10,088 --> 00:23:12,295
<font color=#FFFF00>...untuk bisa menikah.</font>

203
00:23:12,391 --> 00:23:15,702
<font color=#FFFF00>Pengantin wanitanya ingin berpakaian cantik.
Siapa peduli?</font>

204
00:23:15,794 --> 00:23:17,034
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku peduli!</font>

205
00:23:17,562 --> 00:23:23,569
<font color=#FFFF00>Keluarga itu selalu memakai kuilku
untuk semua perayaan mereka!</font>

206
00:23:24,002 --> 00:23:27,779
<font color=#FFFF00>Sekarang, mereka hanya memanggilku
jika ada pemakaman saja.</font>

207
00:23:27,906 --> 00:23:29,613
<font color=#FFFF00>Buddhisme itu...</font>

208
00:23:29,941 --> 00:23:31,943
<font color=#FFFF00>...terlalu menyedihkan.</font>

209
00:23:32,043 --> 00:23:33,613
<font color=#FFFF00>Kalau begitu, bayar uang sewamu!</font>

210
00:23:33,745 --> 00:23:35,952
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa hubungannya dengan itu?</font>

211
00:23:44,055 --> 00:23:47,468
<font color=#FFFF00>Dalam suka ataupun duka,...</font>

212
00:23:48,059 --> 00:23:51,472
<font color=#FFFF00>...apakah kalian berjanji untuk
saling mencintai dan menghormati...</font>

213
00:23:51,730 --> 00:23:54,643
<font color=#FFFF00>...dalam keadaan sehat serta sakit...</font>

214
00:23:55,100 --> 00:24:01,176
<font color=#FFFF00>...sepanjang hidup kalian?</font>

215
00:24:01,273 --> 00:24:02,411
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku bersedia!</font>

216
00:24:02,741 --> 00:24:04,186
<font color=#FFFF00>Dan apakah kau bersedia?</font>

217
00:24:04,476 --> 00:24:05,784
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku bersedia.</font>

218
00:24:05,844 --> 00:24:07,482
<font color=#FFFF00>Amin.</font>

219
00:24:24,296 --> 00:24:26,037
<font color=#FFFF00>Takao-san!</font>

220
00:24:26,331 --> 00:24:29,141
<font color=#FFFF00>Selamat!</font>

221
00:24:38,844 --> 00:24:41,950
<font color=#FFFF00><i>♪ Dulu ada seorang pelaut yang datang
dari tempat yang jauh sekali... ♪</i></font>

222
00:24:42,447 --> 00:24:45,792
<font color=#FFFF00><i>♪ ...datang ke sebuah tempat... ♪</i></font>

223
00:24:46,084 --> 00:24:49,759
<font color=#FFFF00><i>♪ ...di mana tak ada apa pun... ♪</i></font>

224
00:24:50,522 --> 00:24:52,763
<font color=#FFFF00>Selamat!</font>

225
00:24:55,494 --> 00:24:57,030
<font color=#FFFF00>Takao!</font>

226
00:24:58,997 --> 00:25:00,442
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau berhasil!</font>

227
00:25:13,979 --> 00:25:16,152
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku bisa menuangkannya!</font>

228
00:25:16,281 --> 00:25:17,954
<font color=#FFFF00>Ya ampun!</font>

229
00:25:22,587 --> 00:25:28,765
<font color=#FFFF00>Hari ini, dengan segenap restu kalian,
aku bisa menikah di padang rumput yang indah ini.</font>

230
00:25:28,894 --> 00:25:31,431
<font color=#FFFF00>Semua mimpiku telah menjadi kenyataan.</font>

231
00:25:32,531 --> 00:25:37,412
<font color=#FFFF00>Kami bertemu di tur pencarian jodoh
Koperasi Pertanian.</font>

232
00:25:37,536 --> 00:25:39,743
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku berterima kasih pada Eri
karena mau datang ke perkebunan...</font>

233
00:25:39,871 --> 00:25:43,910
<font color=#FFFF00>...yang telah dibangun keluargaku
dengan susah payah.</font>

234
00:25:45,243 --> 00:25:48,417
<font color=#FFFF00>Penantianku selama 45 tahun
tidaklah sia-sia!</font>

235
00:25:58,256 --> 00:26:00,566
<font color=#FFFF00>Takao, berhentilah menangis!</font>

236
00:26:00,992 --> 00:26:02,335
<font color=#FFFF00>Jangan menangis!</font>

237
00:26:05,830 --> 00:26:07,639
<font color=#FFFF00>Takao!</font>

238
00:26:08,166 --> 00:26:14,447
<font color=#FFFF00>Sejak kapan kau menjadi
orang Kristen, sialan!</font>

239
00:26:17,208 --> 00:26:18,152
<font color=#FFFF00>Biksu!</font>

240
00:26:18,276 --> 00:26:19,653
<font color=#FFFF00>Jangan lagi!</font>

241
00:26:21,580 --> 00:26:22,820
<font color=#FFFF00>Dokter!</font>

242
00:26:23,582 --> 00:26:24,856
<font color=#FFFF00>Kemari.</font>

243
00:26:24,983 --> 00:26:25,927
<font color=#FFFF00>Sekarang apa lagi?</font>

244
00:26:25,984 --> 00:26:27,657
<font color=#FFFF00>Cepatlah, Dokter!</font>

245
00:26:30,155 --> 00:26:31,657
<font color=#FFFF00>Ada apa?</font>

246
00:26:33,191 --> 00:26:35,671
<font color=#FFFF00>Biksu! Apa kau baik-baik saja?</font>

247
00:26:39,598 --> 00:26:43,637
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia hanya mabuk.
Beri dia minum air putih.</font>

248
00:26:56,247 --> 00:27:00,320
<font color=#FFFF00>The Cape Village Folk Lovers.</font>

249
00:27:00,385 --> 00:27:02,194
<font color=#FFFF00>Terima kasih banyak.</font>

250
00:27:11,496 --> 00:27:13,567
<font color=#FFFF00>Apakah kau tinggal di sekitar sini?</font>

251
00:27:13,665 --> 00:27:15,201
<font color=#FFFF00>Tuangkan minuman untuk kami.</font>

252
00:27:17,669 --> 00:27:19,080
<font color=#FFFF00>Ayolah!</font>

253
00:27:19,204 --> 00:27:21,206
<font color=#FFFF00>Kami membeli bunga dari Takao.</font>

254
00:27:21,339 --> 00:27:22,249
<font color=#FFFF00>Tolong hentikan!</font>

255
00:27:30,682 --> 00:27:31,752
<font color=#FFFF00>Heh, setan!</font>

256
00:27:31,883 --> 00:27:34,193
<font color=#FFFF00>Singkirkan tangan kotormu darinya!</font>

257
00:27:44,829 --> 00:27:46,900
<font color=#FFFF00>Koji!</font>

258
00:27:47,032 --> 00:27:49,512
<font color=#FFFF00>Mundurlah.</font>

259
00:27:53,538 --> 00:27:54,380
<font color=#FFFF00>Koji!</font>

260
00:27:54,506 --> 00:27:57,510
<font color=#FFFF00>Mereka adalah pelangganku!</font>

261
00:27:58,443 --> 00:28:00,753
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau menghancurkan acara pernikahanku!</font>

262
00:28:12,724 --> 00:28:17,366
<font color=#FFFF00>Kapan kau akan dewasa?
Kau selalu mengulangi perbuatanmu!</font>

263
00:28:17,462 --> 00:28:20,341
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia berusaha melindungimu...</font>

264
00:28:20,465 --> 00:28:22,035
<font color=#FFFF00>Yah, terima kasih banyak!</font>

265
00:28:23,702 --> 00:28:26,740
<font color=#FFFF00>Sekarang, aku malu dengan warga desa!</font>

266
00:28:27,272 --> 00:28:29,445
<font color=#FFFF00>Tolong maafkan dia, ya?</font>

267
00:28:30,608 --> 00:28:31,951
<font color=#FFFF00>Minta maaflah.</font>

268
00:28:35,613 --> 00:28:39,288
<font color=#FFFF00>Koji! Ayo kita main lempar tangkap lagi.</font>

269
00:28:39,417 --> 00:28:40,521
<font color=#FFFF00>Baik?</font>

270
00:28:43,755 --> 00:28:45,962
<font color=#FFFF00>Ayo.</font>

271
00:28:47,158 --> 00:28:48,228
<font color=#FFFF00>Lempar bolanya!</font>

272
00:28:49,627 --> 00:28:51,106
<font color=#FFFF00>Nice ball!</font>

273
00:28:51,196 --> 00:28:54,200
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau memang Sang Bintang
dari SMA Cape!</font>

274
00:29:01,740 --> 00:29:06,587
<font color=#FFFF00>Jika bahumu tak cedera, kau pasti
sudah memenangi Kejuaraan Nasional!</font>

275
00:29:16,654 --> 00:29:18,361
<font color=#FFFF00>Lempar yang keras!</font>

276
00:29:21,826 --> 00:29:22,827
<font color=#FFFF00>Terima ini.</font>

277
00:29:22,927 --> 00:29:24,634
<font color=#FFFF00>Cepat lempar.</font>

278
00:29:26,865 --> 00:29:28,310
<font color=#FFFF00>Nice ball!</font>

279
00:29:28,433 --> 00:29:29,776
<font color=#FFFF00>Hei, Bos!</font>

280
00:29:29,834 --> 00:29:30,744
<font color=#FFFF00>Jangan ribut!</font>

281
00:29:30,835 --> 00:29:32,007
<font color=#FFFF00>Ada masalah!</font>

282
00:29:32,103 --> 00:29:33,446
<font color=#FFFF00>Ibumu mati?</font>

283
00:29:33,505 --> 00:29:35,485
<font color=#FFFF00>Jangan begitu pada Ibuku!</font>

284
00:29:36,174 --> 00:29:39,348
<font color=#FFFF00>Kucing Narikawa-san
terjebak lagi di atas pohon.</font>

285
00:29:40,745 --> 00:29:42,019
<font color=#FFFF00>Momo?</font>

286
00:29:42,514 --> 00:29:45,290
<font color=#FFFF00>Mereka melepaskannya?</font>

287
00:29:45,817 --> 00:29:48,798
<font color=#FFFF00>Hanya kau yang bisa menurunkannya.</font>

288
00:29:49,120 --> 00:29:51,100
<font color=#FFFF00>Mereka memintamu cepat datang.</font>

289
00:29:51,389 --> 00:29:53,699
<font color=#FFFF00>Oh, baiklah...</font>

290
00:29:54,959 --> 00:29:56,461
<font color=#FFFF00>Kalian mendengar dia.</font>

291
00:29:56,594 --> 00:29:59,507
<font color=#FFFF00>Sampai nanti, Tani-san.</font>

292
00:29:59,597 --> 00:30:01,406
<font color=#FFFF00>Pergantian pemain.</font>

293
00:30:01,533 --> 00:30:04,514
<font color=#FFFF00>Yang melempar sekarang,
Kashiwagi Etsuko!</font>

294
00:30:20,585 --> 00:30:22,929
<font color=#FFFF00>Terima kasih, Tani-san.</font>

295
00:30:24,422 --> 00:30:27,699
<font color=#FFFF00>Karena telah berpura-pura
memercayai cerita Koji.</font>

296
00:30:28,693 --> 00:30:29,831
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia bilang...</font>

297
00:30:30,829 --> 00:30:33,537
<font color=#FFFF00>...dia telah berjanji pada suamimu.</font>

298
00:30:34,365 --> 00:30:40,008
<font color=#FFFF00>"Saat mau meninggal, dia menggenggam
tanganku dan bilang, 'Jagalah Etsuko'."</font>

299
00:30:41,072 --> 00:30:45,452
<font color=#FFFF00>"Dan aku meremas tangannya dan bilang,
'Jangan khawatir, Paman.'"</font>

300
00:30:45,877 --> 00:30:49,324
<font color=#FFFF00>"'Aku akan menjaga Et-chan untukmu.'"</font>

301
00:30:53,685 --> 00:30:57,827
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku jadi bingung saat kau bilang
itu tak pernah terjadi.</font>

302
00:30:57,922 --> 00:31:01,734
<font color=#FFFF00>Tapi kalau masalah dia yang
mengkhawatirkanmu, itu benar.</font>

303
00:31:04,629 --> 00:31:05,767
<font color=#FFFF00>Lempar bolanya!</font>

304
00:31:13,071 --> 00:31:14,846
<font color=#FFFF00>Nice ball!</font>

305
00:32:27,111 --> 00:32:28,215
<font color=#FFFF00>Siapa di situ?!</font>

306
00:32:38,890 --> 00:32:40,494
<font color=#FFFF00>Lihat yang kau perbuat!</font>

307
00:32:40,658 --> 00:32:42,660
<font color=#FFFF00>Jangan mendekat!</font>

308
00:32:55,073 --> 00:32:56,643
<font color=#FFFF00>Jangan berisik.</font>

309
00:32:56,774 --> 00:32:59,118
<font color=#FFFF00>Berikan uangmu.</font>

310
00:33:02,180 --> 00:33:04,319
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku tidak berisik.</font>

311
00:33:05,450 --> 00:33:07,657
<font color=#FFFF00>Uang!</font>

312
00:33:10,288 --> 00:33:13,701
<font color=#FFFF00>Uangnya ada di mesin kasir, Pak.</font>

313
00:33:14,058 --> 00:33:15,560
<font color=#FFFF00>"Pak"?</font>

314
00:33:16,127 --> 00:33:17,936
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa kau tahu aku ini apa?</font>

315
00:33:18,062 --> 00:33:20,508
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau adalah maling, ya 'kan?</font>

316
00:33:21,232 --> 00:33:23,735
<font color=#FFFF00>Iya.</font>

317
00:33:25,703 --> 00:33:29,549
<font color=#FFFF00>Semua uang yang kumiliki
ada di mesin kasir.</font>

318
00:33:29,640 --> 00:33:31,017
<font color=#FFFF00>Maafkan aku.</font>

319
00:33:33,144 --> 00:33:36,023
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau meminta maaf?</font>

320
00:33:38,383 --> 00:33:41,853
<font color=#FFFF00>Apakah ini pertama kalinya
kau mencuri?</font>

321
00:33:42,720 --> 00:33:44,825
<font color=#FFFF00>Iya.</font>

322
00:33:47,859 --> 00:33:50,863
<font color=#FFFF00>Tapi kau malah mencuri di tempat
yang tidak memiliki uang!</font>

323
00:34:01,606 --> 00:34:02,949
<font color=#FFFF00>Kelihatannya kau lapar.</font>

324
00:34:13,951 --> 00:34:15,430
<font color=#FFFF00>Mm...</font>

325
00:34:16,854 --> 00:34:17,924
<font color=#FFFF00>Kenapa?</font>

326
00:34:20,458 --> 00:34:24,338
<font color=#FFFF00>Tadi kau memandangi lukisan itu.</font>

327
00:34:26,030 --> 00:34:29,944
<font color=#FFFF00>Jadi, aku berpikir kalau
kau tak mungkin orang jahat...</font>

328
00:34:30,268 --> 00:34:35,946
<font color=#FFFF00>...jika kau mau mencuri tapi
malah terkesima melihat lukisan.</font>

329
00:34:39,410 --> 00:34:40,889
<font color=#FFFF00>Dengar, Pak...</font>

330
00:34:43,281 --> 00:34:48,094
<font color=#FFFF00>Jika kau sedang memiliki masalah,
ambillah lukisan itu.</font>

331
00:34:49,253 --> 00:34:52,234
<font color=#FFFF00>Meskipun itu tak akan terjual mahal.</font>

332
00:34:54,859 --> 00:34:59,535
<font color=#FFFF00>Suamiku yang melukisnya.
Dulu dia adalah seorang pelukis.</font>

333
00:34:59,931 --> 00:35:01,376
<font color=#FFFF00>"Dulu"?</font>

334
00:35:03,868 --> 00:35:07,475
<font color=#FFFF00>Suamiku sudah lama meninggal.</font>

335
00:35:08,706 --> 00:35:10,845
<font color=#FFFF00>Itu adalah lukisan terakhirnya.</font>

336
00:35:12,844 --> 00:35:18,351
<font color=#FFFF00>Lukisan itu dan isi mesin kasir ini saja
yang berharga di tempat ini.</font>

337
00:35:20,918 --> 00:35:22,488
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku tak bisa.</font>

338
00:35:22,854 --> 00:35:26,028
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku tak bisa mengambil
barang seberharga itu.</font>

339
00:35:26,357 --> 00:35:27,335
<font color=#FFFF00>Tapi...</font>

340
00:35:42,673 --> 00:35:46,382
<font color=#FFFF00>Kenapa aku bisa sampai melakukan ini?</font>

341
00:35:48,846 --> 00:35:51,417
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa yang kulakukan?</font>

342
00:35:56,854 --> 00:35:58,299
<font color=#FFFF00>Katakan padaku, Pak...</font>

343
00:35:59,090 --> 00:36:00,433
<font color=#FFFF00>Ya?</font>

344
00:36:01,425 --> 00:36:04,929
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa pekerjaanmu yang sesungguhnya?</font>

345
00:36:08,599 --> 00:36:12,411
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku pengasah pisau.</font>

346
00:36:15,740 --> 00:36:20,052
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku mengambil alih toko Ayahku,
tapi toko itu kini sudah bangkrut.</font>

347
00:36:21,078 --> 00:36:23,080
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku sedang terlilit hutang.</font>

348
00:36:24,448 --> 00:36:27,952
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku akan kehilangan toko
dan juga rumahku.</font>

349
00:36:34,792 --> 00:36:37,534
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku sempat memikirkan untuk
melakukan bunuh diri sekeluarga,...</font>

350
00:36:39,063 --> 00:36:44,376
<font color=#FFFF00>...tapi saat melihat wajah putriku,
aku tak sanggup melakukannya.</font>

351
00:36:45,469 --> 00:36:51,613
<font color=#FFFF00>Lalu aku sempat berpikir untuk gantung diri
dan meninggalkan istri serta putriku.</font>

352
00:36:52,076 --> 00:36:54,454
<font color=#FFFF00>Tapi dahan pohonnya patah.</font>

353
00:36:55,947 --> 00:36:58,689
<font color=#FFFF00>Dan sekarang aku juga
telah gagal menjadi maling.</font>

354
00:37:00,051 --> 00:37:02,361
<font color=#FFFF00>Untunglah kau gagal.</font>

355
00:37:03,621 --> 00:37:09,264
<font color=#FFFF00>Jika kau berhasil, baik kau maupun
keluargamu tak akan ada di sini.</font>

356
00:37:11,762 --> 00:37:13,332
<font color=#FFFF00>Begitu, ya.</font>

357
00:37:15,166 --> 00:37:16,839
<font color=#FFFF00>Anda benar.</font>

358
00:37:17,768 --> 00:37:20,908
<font color=#FFFF00>Terkadang tak apa untuk gagal.</font>

359
00:37:42,660 --> 00:37:47,473
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Aku akan menjalani hidup baru
dengan istri serta anakku.</i></font>

360
00:37:48,633 --> 00:37:52,945
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Ini adalah pisau tertajam
yang pernah aku asah.</i></font>

361
00:37:53,971 --> 00:37:56,178
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Aku memberikannya untuk bilang,...</i></font>

362
00:37:57,108 --> 00:38:01,181
<font color=#FFFF00><i>..."Terima kasih banyak".
Tertanda, Maling.</i></font>

363
00:38:21,265 --> 00:38:24,371
<font color=#FFFF00>Koji-san! Kau sedang apa?</font>

364
00:38:24,468 --> 00:38:29,713
<font color=#FFFF00>Tepat waktu sekali, Yama!
Mulai hari ini, kau pindah ke sini.</font>

365
00:38:29,813 --> 00:38:30,563
<font color=#FFFF00>Hah?!</font>

366
00:38:30,574 --> 00:38:31,746
<font color=#FFFF00>Bukan hah-heh hah-heh.</font>

367
00:38:32,143 --> 00:38:37,217
<font color=#FFFF00>Rumah Et-chan dibobol maling.
Dia bisa saja terbunuh.</font>

368
00:38:37,548 --> 00:38:40,757
<font color=#FFFF00>Jika pos polisi ada di sini,
itu tak akan terjadi lagi.</font>

